column5: I plan on taking 18 credits the next four semesters. I took 31 credits last year.

I understand. I have OCD (with germs) and I am now terrified to get back to normal life. Going to college in the fall scared me and starting my summer job in June makes me very anxious. It doesn’t help that my mother fought breast cancer last year, so she is immunocompromised-in the high risk group. Message me if you need to talk. I feel your pain.
